Entries.default: "My, my - aren't you a handsome one." An older woman looks you up and down and smiles, revealing several gold teeth.
Entries.female: "My, my - aren't you a pretty one." An older woman looks you up and down and smiles, revealing several gold teeth.

Entries.default: "Always a pleasure to see you again, dear." She winks.
"Did you need... help with something, my dear?"
"My pleasure." She grins, showing off her golden teeth, and leads you to a couch.
"Isn't it obvious? I entertain, of course!" She does a little shimmy and breaks off with a laugh.
"It'll cost you fifty pires, naturally. And don't let the wrinkles fool you - I'm still young at heart, and I've got more experience than most." She chuckles.
